dmca.title: DMCA Violation - finland-international.dk
dmca.body:
Dear Sir or Madam:

This letter is to notify you, pursuant to the provisions of the Digital Millennium Copyright Act, that we believe one of your customers is infringing gameraid.net's and loaguild.com's, a division of Video Game Files Network, Inc. ("V.G.F. NET"), copyrighted materials. Specifically, gameraid.net and loaguild.com is the owner of the copyright and trademarked materials.

The following site hosts and is distributing webpages and content created by us that violates V.G.F. NET's copyrights and trademarks: 
http://finland-international.dk

The aforementioned site either hosts or distributes our webpages without authorization, which illegally modifies and/or alters V.G.F. NET copyrighted materials, thereby infringing upon V.G.F. NET's copyrights and trademarks. 

Accordingly, V.G.F. NET demands that you act expeditiously to remove, or disable access to, the web page listed above in order for you to claim a safe harbor under the DMCA from liability for contributory and vicarious copyright infringement. Please immediately delete or disable access to this web page and remove its contents from view. Should you have any questions, please contact the undersigned at piracy@gameraid.net. 

I have a good faith belief that use of the material in the manner complained of is not authorized by V.G.F. NET's, its agents or the law, and that the information in this notice is accurate. I declare under penalty of perjury under the laws of the United States of America that I am authorized to act on behalf of all of the aforementioned entities. 

Sincerely,

V.G.F. NET Administrator
